{"title":"在Ubuntu（Linux）下 使用Let's Encrypt免费SSL证书，实现全站HTTPS","date":"2018-02-05T04:30:18.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 5, 2018","L":"02/05/2018","MM-DD":"02-05"},"link":"Learning/ef95baa65b1c","tags":["Let's Encrypt","SSL","免费SSL证书"],"categories":["Learning"],"updated":"2021-02-27T13:47:30.058Z","content":"<p>Let’s Encrypt免费SSL证书，实现全站HTTPS</p>\n<h2 id=\"第一步：安装git\">第一步：安装git<a title=\"#第一步：安装git\" href=\"#第一步：安装git\"></a></h2>\n<p>执行以下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"第二步：获取let's-encrypt免费ssl证书(会自动配置环境)\">第二步：获取Let’s Encrypt免费SSL证书(会自动配置环境)<a title=\"#第二步：获取let's-encrypt免费ssl证书(会自动配置环境)\" href=\"#第二步：获取let's-encrypt免费ssl证书(会自动配置环境)\"></a></h2>\n<p>执行以下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/letsencrypt/letsencrypt</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> letsencrypt</span><br><span class=\"line\">./letsencrypt-auto</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>期间会提示输入你的邮箱，然后一路a(agree),y(yes)。 站点选择的时候， 开通对应站点前的数字即可，如果空着的话，就代表主机上的站点全部开通。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"修改WordPress主题字体，使用自定义TTF字体","link":"Learning/f0c1e4e6fd81"},"next":{"title":"Dream","link":"Learning/b59c9330cdff"},"plink":"https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/ef95baa65b1c/","toc":[{"id":"第一步：安装git","title":"第一步：安装git","index":"1"},{"id":"第二步：获取let's-encrypt免费ssl证书(会自动配置环境)","title":"第二步：获取Let’s Encrypt免费SSL证书(会自动配置环境)","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Patrick Jun","link":"<a href=\"https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/ef95baa65b1c/\" title=\"在Ubuntu（Linux）下 使用Let's Encrypt免费SSL证书，实现全站HTTPS\">https://www.zzboy.cn/Learnin